Steps to build nvflash.exe in Visual Studio.

1. Download and install Visual studio if not already installed.
2. Install perforce for windows if not already installed.
3. Get the latest revision of software tools in local folder required to build nvflash.exe from perforce and set this path to $PERFORCE_WORKSPACE 
4. Edit bsp_build_nvflash.bat to set WDK_ROOT_DIR = $PERFORCE_WORKSPACE\<sw-tools-dir> and DEVENV_COMMAND according to the version of Visual Studio.
5. Run bsp_build_nvflash.bat, it will open visual studio with nvflash.sln solution.
6. Build nvflash.sln, nvflash.exe will be created.
